                    <li> <span class="text-primary">@nameof(NWDWebStandardConfiguration.AppleKeyValue)</span> and insert the value of the file, removing the <code>`-----BEGIN PRIVATE KEY-----`</code> and <code>`-----END PRIVATE KEY-----`</code> prefix and suffix, and insert line by line in a string array. </li>
